<TEXT>Handles well and is larger than the Honda. Test drove both vans and the Sienna was the best van at a much lower price. We have three small children and thus three car seats. The Sienna has ample room for all the kids and plenty of room for cargo. Roof rack is standard equipment which is also a plus. I would recommend this van to anyone.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>New gear shift console and dash layout. The interior is very comfortable and has plenty of room.</FAVORITE>
